abstract.text: An immutable object that combines a contact property value with a label that describes that property.

inlineContent.text: Labels describe the context for a property. For example, the label for a phone number indicates whether it corresponds to the user’s home, work, or iPhone number.
objects are thread-safe, and you can access their properties from any thread of your app.
